Auxiliary Ships are designed to operate in any number of roles supporting combatant ships and other naval operations.  Although they have combat capacity, Auxiliaries are not primary combatants and are usually used for self-defense instead.


=== List of Auxiliary Ship Types seen in KanColle: ===
*Amphibious Assault Ship (LHA)
*Fleet Oiler (AO)
*Repair Ship (AR)
*Seaplane Tender (AV)
*Submarine Tender (AS)
*Training Cruiser (CT)
